<section id="about" class="relative py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <p class="section-header mb-12">
      <span class="text-glow-amber">&gt;</span> about
    </p>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Photo column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 flex justify-center lg:justify-start">
        <div class="crt-vignette rounded-lg overflow-hidden w-64 h-64 lg:w-full lg:h-auto lg:aspect-square bg-screen-panel border border-screen-raised">
          <!-- Placeholder for photo -->
          <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center text-text-faint font-mono text-xs">
            [ photo ]
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio column -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3">
        <!-- Pull quote -->
        <blockquote class="font-mono text-glow-amber text-sm mb-8 pl-4 border-l-2 border-glow-amber/30">
          "I thrive on untangling complex problems and designing elegant,
          scalable systems."
        </blockquote>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            I'm a full-stack engineer based in Gilbert, Arizona with a
            path that's anything but typical. I started in
            <span class="text-text-bright">finance</span> — earned my BS
            from the University of Arizona — then found my real passion
            building software. I went back for a
            <span class="text-text-bright">CS degree from WGU</span> and
            never looked back.
          </p>
          <p>
            That dual perspective is my edge. I don't just write code — I
            understand the business context it lives in. Today I'm
            architecting infrastructure from the ground up at B1 Marketing
            Group while building
            <span class="text-neon-cyan">Balance</span>, a HIPAA-compliant
            medical billing platform that's helped clients increase their
            30-day collections from 30% to 70%.
          </p>
          <p>
            When I'm not deep in a codebase, you'll find me watching hoops,
            hunting down the best sushi spot, or playing games with my
            daughter and our two Labs. I grew up on retro consoles and that
            love for pixel art and classic game design still shows up in
            everything I build — including this site.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
